	  <value>Bads at low health let you live for roughly 3x as long as misses, this gap increases the higher the life threshold you want to keep, up to misses punishing 6x as much when maintaining 100% visual life.</value>
  </data>
  <data name="TLDR: Misses matter less at low life, but are always significantly more punishing than Bads." xml:space="preserve">
	  <value>TLDR: Misses matter less at low life, but are always significantly more punishing than Bads.</value>
  </data>
